# Privacy Policy – SZ Ride Book

Last updated: 05 February 2026

SZ Ride Book (“we”, “our”, “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use the SZ Ride Book mobile application.

## Information We Collect

We may collect the following data:

* Name and phone number for user verification
* Vehicle booking details and ride history
* Location data for booking and tracking rides
* Device and app usage data for performance and security
* QR code scan data for booking verification

## How We Use Your Data

Your data is used to:

* Enable vehicle booking and ride management
* Verify users and bookings
* Track booking history
* Improve app performance and user experience
* Prevent fraud and misuse

## Data Sharing

We do not sell or rent user data.
Data may be shared only with trusted third-party services such as Firebase and Google services for authentication, database storage, and analytics.

## Children’s Privacy

SZ Ride Book does not knowingly collect personal data from children under the age of 13. If such data is identified, it will be deleted immediately.

## Data Security

We use industry-standard security measures to protect user information from unauthorized access or disclosure.

## User Rights

Users may request access, correction, or deletion of their personal data by contacting us.

## Changes to This Policy

This policy may be updated periodically. Updates will be posted on this page.


